⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Godrick the Grafted
node ER · ER · ⟦Godrick the Grafted:ER:6e6c09⟧

WHO   — Godrick the Grafted — the lowest of the golden line, grown monstrous by grafting
WHAT  — A distant, diminished scion of the golden lineage who holds Stormveil Castle, grown monstrous by grafting.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: Stormveil Castle and the golden lineage's decayed remnant  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — The first great shardbearer most players face — the dynasty's decay made flesh.
HOW   — Grafts the limbs of slain Tarnished onto his own body — dozens of arms and legs — to counterfeit the strength his blood lacks.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  He who lacked strength stole a hundred arms to grasp it, and grasped only rot.

